cn.inbot.navigationlib.event

类 OnInquiryRelocateEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.inbot.navigationlib.event.OnInquiryRelocateEvent

  • public class OnInquiryRelocateEvent
extends java.lang.Object

    Inquiry relocate event

    充电时重定位事件类

    This event will be posted when the robot is charging and the current position of the robot is far away from the charging point.
    当机器人靠上充电底座时，如果机器人在地图上的位置与充电底座较远，则会通过EventBus抛出此事件对象。

    Author : Inbot
    Create Date : 2020/03/17
    JDK version used : JDK1.8
    Version : V1.0.0
    Copyright ©2020 Inbot Technology Ltd. All rights reserved.
